<!-- 규칙 추가 Window에서 연간 RadioButton 클릭하면 오른쪽 공간에 구성되는 View -->
<UserControl x:Class="TODO_List.View.AddTodo.Routine.YearlyRoutineView"
                   xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
                   xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml">
    <Border>
        <Grid>
            <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
                <RowDefinition Height="*"/>
            </Grid.RowDefinitions>

            <StackPanel Grid.Row="0" Orientation="Horizontal" Margin="0,0,0,10">
                <TextBlock Text="날짜 선택: " VerticalAlignment="Center" FontWeight="Bold" Margin="0,0,5,0"/>
                <DatePicker SelectedDate="{Binding SelectedTempDate}" Style="{StaticResource YearlyRoutineDatePicker}"/>
                <Button Content="등록" Margin="5,0,5,0" Command="{Binding DateRegisterCommand}"/>
            </StackPanel>

            <Grid Grid.Row="1">
                <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                    <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
                    <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                <ListBox Grid.Column="0" Style="{StaticResource YearlySelectedDaysListBox}"
                            ItemsSource="{Binding SelectedYearlyDates}" x:Name="SelectedDaysListBox"/>

                <StackPanel Orientation="Vertical" Grid.Column="1" Grid.Row="0" VerticalAlignment="Top">
                    <Button Content="제거" Margin="5,0,0,5" Height="22.5" VerticalAlignment="Top"
                                Command="{Binding DateRemoveCommand}"
                                CommandParameter="{Binding SelectedItems, ElementName=SelectedDaysListBox}"/>
                    <Button Content="초기화" Margin="5,0,0,5" Height="22.5" VerticalAlignment="Top"
                                Command="{Binding DatesClearCommand}"/>
                </StackPanel>
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
    </Border>
</UserControl>